e resistance changing as\n$T^{\\rm n}$, with n=1.6, whereas it becomes a normal Fermi-liquid, n = 2, for\npressures above $\\sim$15 GPa. On the basis of the obtained data a magnetic\nphase diagram in the ($p$, $T$) space is suggested.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 May 2015 09:28:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
